{"tid":23551,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"(離巢王)陳國邦為藝術忍痛宣佈離開無線!!!!!!!!!","createTime":"2016-12-05T04:07:01.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-05T09:15:59.000Z","uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"adb348be421e216977e6e1d1cabf155788253752","tid":23551,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T04:07:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/apple-photos/apple/20161205/large/05ec3p6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20161205%2Flarge%2F05ec3p6.jpg&h=0e71bae9&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n陳國邦去年撰寫「公開辭職信」宣佈離開無綫，但兩個月後被毛舜筠打動，接演處境劇《愛．回家之八時入席》，與公司簽一年約。一年過去，有傳毛姐不滿淪為配角，令《八》不再添食，國邦亦再次宣佈離巢。 <br />\n<br />\n即將約滿的國邦昨在電話中說： 「公司有同我傾，但我想做番我嘅藝術工作者。」他坦言心情輕鬆，而太太羅敏莊都支持。"},{"pid":"bc155cb06787291b69016a675797d988514a76fa","tid":23551,"uid":43358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T04:09:22.000Z","msg":"幾個月後會重返TVB大家庭啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0fa8b35fea641a10352c9d1a250f09cb66ffdbc","tid":23551,"uid":29167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T04:10:02.000Z","msg":"森哥又玩乜鳩 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e51acbc7f39a9e174a1181b41a627535715a28a","tid":23551,"uid":20815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T04:18:03.000Z","msg":"離巢王<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b8b734e4a532cfae7608224189f50578c1117cd","tid":23551,"uid":294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T04:20:13.000Z","msg":"果然係文種<br />\n唔識人情世故"},{"pid":"4850f6fad2791d56f1bf63e85d18bbdc567742cd","tid":23551,"uid":40272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T04:21:49.000Z","msg":"香港宮崎駿"},{"pid":"488071c6b0b0b2fab0759cfaf5168fe2e2b0d6f3","tid":23551,"uid":759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":